description: The XY series is based on the events of the Generation VI games. As with the previous three series, the XY series begins with only http://anidb.net/ch6693 [Ash Ketchum] heading off to a new region with his http://anidb.net/ch8091 [Pikachu]; his previous companions, http://anidb.net/ch21697 [Iris] and http://anidb.net/ch21700 [Cilan], have left the series. Ash`s journey through the Kalos Region begins in Lumiose City, and soon he will be joined by http://anidb.net/ch61303 [Serena], http://anidb.net/ch61305 [Clemont], and http://anidb.net/ch61304 [Bonnie].
